node.text:
We're back on tour!!! We are extremely excited to kick off The Impractical Jokers Scoopski Potatoes Tour in arenas this fall! Tickets for all dates will be available at TheTenderloins.com/Tour, linked in my bio. Pre-sale begins Wednesday for select cities, with ALL SHOWS ON SALE THIS FRIDAY! Find your city below in the list and tag someone you are bringing with you! 
 
2021:
11/19 Glendale, AZ - Gila River Arena
11/20 San Diego, CA - Pechanga Arena
11/21 Sacramento, CA - Golden 1 Center
12/3 Minneapolis, MN - Target Center
12/4 Green Bay, WI - Resch Center
12/17 Milwaukee, WI - Fiserv Forum
12/18  Kansas City, MO - T-Mobile Center
12/19 Sioux Falls, SD - PREMIER Center
12/28 Cincinnati, OH - Heritage Bank Center
12/29 Cleveland, OH - Rocket Mortgage Fieldhouse
12/30 Columbus, OH - Schottenstein Center
12/31 Chicago, IL - United Center

2022:
2/10 Boise, ID - ExtraMile Arena
2/11  Portland, OR - Moda Center
2/27 Jacksonville, FL - Vystar Veterans Memorial Arena
3/26  Duluth, GA - Gas South Arena
4/29 Albany, NY - Times Union Center
4/30 Wilkes-Barre, PA - Mohegan Sun Arena at Casey Plaza
7/1 Salt Lake City, UT - Vivint Arena
7/14 St. Louis, MO - Enterprise Center
7/15 Oklahoma City, OK - Chesapeake Energy Arena
7/16 Fort Worth, TX - Dickies Arena
7/24 Costa Mesa, CA - Orange County Fair – Pacific Amphitheater
7/29 Syracuse, NY - Oncenter War Memorial Arena
8/6 Lincoln, NE - Pinnacle Bank Arena
8/17  Pittsburgh, PA - PPG Paints Arena
8/19 Norfolk, VA - Scope Arena
 
**All rescheduled tickets will be honored if purchased through authorized seller.
